data.description: You're not going to want to miss your chance on this great ranch home in Grimes! From a great lot, location, open plan, finished basement and plenty of updates, this home is ready for you to call it home! The main level features its large open great room that is perfect for entertaining or for spending time with the family! Down the hall you'll will find the three main bedrooms along with large full bath. The master suite is conveniently tucked away in its own corner for privacy from the common areas and includes an en suite bath and large walk-in closet! Be sure to head down to the newly redone basement where you'll find another full bed and bath, lots of storage room and the second living area! There is even a wet bar! So many possibilities from a man cave, to a playroom or even a movie room for the whole family! Out back you'll find the elevated deck that overlooks the walking path and the yard is already fully fenced in as well! This is the home for you! Schedule your private showing today, don't miss out!!
